Sir Terry Pratchett's final Discworld novel will be released in September .
The book will feature Tiffany Aching, a witch-in-training who has featured in four of Sir Terry's books to date .
Book will be called The Shepherd's Crown and feature Tiffany's grandmother .
It will be set in the fictional world of Discworld - a flat disc balanced on four elephants and a giant turtle roaming through space .